## Firth's adjusted scores methods

::: {.nudge-up}
Instead of solving [$s(\vartheta)=0$]{.text-org}, solve [$s(\vartheta) + \overbrace{A(\vartheta)}^{\mathcal B(\vartheta) I(\vartheta)}=0$]{.text-tur}.
